desc: Keepin' Slim Cans cold like it our job! The HOOCH|HOG "Skinny" fits all slim cans including White Claw, Michelob Ultra, Truly, Redbull, LaCroix, etc. This stainless steel can cooler keeps beverages cold for 6+ hours. It's easy to grab, lighter weight and comfortable enough to hold all day. Voted Best Grip Can Cooler.
